# Dtype-parameterized 4-wave conv correctness tests. Single source
# file (`test_amd_4wave_conv_dtypes.mojo`); one `mojo_test` target per
# dtype, each with `-D DTYPE=<dtype>`. Black-box correctness check of
# `amd_4wave_conv` vs `structured_4wave_matmul` on a host-materialized
